headline: DC judge delivers smackdown to Airbnb squatter after ruling she has no tenancy. Homeowner rights finally defended?
summary: Rochanne Douglas's nightmare began when Romero booked her furnished home through Airbnb, claiming her own apartment had been damaged in a fire. Here's what Douglas didn't know.
